         <div xml:id="bHY6yh-d43598"><!-- p2l6-r9 -->
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d43598-Hd1e108">Rubrica 9</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d43598-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De placiditate et ferocitate regis et iudicis</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d43598-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="32"/>
      ¶ De placiditate et ferocita
      <lb ed="#V" n="33" break="no"/>te regis et iudicis. Rubrica. 9.
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d43598-d1e121">
               <lb ed="#V" n="34"/><ref>Seneca de clementia:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHy6yh-d43598-Qd1e123">Ma
      <lb ed="#V" n="35" break="no"/>gni animi proprium est pla
      <lb ed="#V" n="36" break="no"/>cidum esse et tranquillum quietumque.</quote> 
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d43598-d1e130">
               <lb ed="#V" n="37"/>
             ¶ <ref>Lex diges. ti. de offi. praesi l. obser
        <lb ed="#V" n="38" break="no"/>uandum:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d43598-Qd1e134">Obseruandum est ius reddenti: vt in
        <lb ed="#V" n="39"/>adeundo: quod facile se praebeat: sed conteruisse non
        <lb ed="#V" n="40"/>patiatur. Iudex in cognoscendo neque excande
        <lb ed="#V" n="41" break="no"/>scere debet aduersus eos quos malos putat
        <lb ed="#V" n="42"/>neque praecibus calamitosorum illachrimari opor
        <lb ed="#V" n="43" break="no"/>tet: id enim non est recti et constantis iudicis cu
        <lb ed="#V" n="44" break="no"/>ius animi motum vultus detegit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d43598-d1e154">
               <lb ed="#V" n="45"/>
             ¶ <ref>Auctor libri de formula honeste vite. c. 8.</ref> <!--141.xml-->
        <cb ed="#V" n="b"/>
                  <lb ed="#V" n="46"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d43598-Qd1e158">Seuerior esto iudicio quam sermone: vita quam
        <lb ed="#V" n="47"/>vultu.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d43598-d1e170">
               <lb ed="#V" n="48"/>
             ¶ <ref>Claudianus li. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d43598-Qd1e174">Peragit tranquilla potestas.
        <lb ed="#V" n="49"/>Quod violenta nequit: mandataque fortius vrget
        <lb ed="#V" n="50"/>Imperiosa quies.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d43598-d1e182"> /
               <ref>Libro. 8.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="51"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d43598-Qd1e184">Publicus hinc ardescit: amor cum moribus
        <lb ed="#V" n="52"/>equis. Inclinat populo regale modestia culmen</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d43598-d1e192">
               <lb ed="#V" n="53"/>
             ¶ <ref>Cassiodorus epistolarum li. 6. e. 24. et pe.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d43598-Qd1e196">Utrum
        <lb ed="#V" n="54" break="no"/>que laudabile est: vt bonus populus iudicem
        <lb ed="#V" n="55"/>benignum faciat: et mansuetus iudex: grauissi
        <lb ed="#V" n="56" break="no"/>mum populum equabili ratione componat.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d43598-d1e206"> /
               <ref>Li. 10:
        <lb ed="#V" n="57"/>e. 7.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d43598-Qd1e208">Iudiciaria virtus est: lingue bonis abun
        <lb ed="#V" n="58" break="no"/>dare: et mentis temperantia custodire.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d43598-d1e216">
               <lb ed="#V" n="59"/>
             ¶ <ref>Gregorius in pastorali. ca. 18.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d43598-Qd1e220">Sit rector
        <lb ed="#V" n="60"/>bene agentibus per humilitatem socius: contra
        <lb ed="#V" n="61"/>delinquentium vitia per zelum iustitie erectus.
        <lb ed="#V" n="62"/>Summus locus bene regitur: cum is qui praest vi
        <lb ed="#V" n="63" break="no"/>tiis. potius quam fratribus dominatur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d43598-d1e233">
               <lb ed="#V" n="64"/>
             ¶ <ref>Gualterius de castellione lib. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d43598-Qd1e237">Ciuiliter
        <lb ed="#V" n="65"/>argue sontes.</quote>
            </p>
